creator: Wedbox Wedding Apps
descriptionHtml:
We have created a beautiful wedding photo app, that lets your guests collect pictures and videos from your wedding.

The app will automatically categorize your pictures in categories that you have set up.

With the app you will get this:

- All your guests can upload pictures and videos before, during and after the wedding
- Its a closed forum between you and the guests you invite into the app.
- You can create a slideshow with the wedding pictures
- The guests can comment and like the wedding photos and videos
- App will be translated to 18 languages by march 2017
- The app is for sharing pictures and videos and nothing else. This way we have been able to keep app simple and beautiful
- All copyrights stays with you, and we do not use your pictures for anything
- The quality of the pictures are not diminished
- The app is free for you and for your guests
- Use is for your wedding and for your bachelor/ette party

Keep an eye out for updates to the app, as we are constantly developing the app.

This app is the best wedding photo app on the market

If you have guests from many countries and you want to collect their photos and videos as well for the wedding, we recommend inviting them as well in the app.

The app is more than just a photo app, you can use it to communicate with your guests as well.

Some weddings use the apps slideshow feature and cast pictures on a big screen during the wedding or play a fun game with guests and ask them to take certain photos during the day.

We also see many users using the app for bachelor or bachelorette parties and printing all pictures through our print service after the event. The printed photobook can be used as a great gift for the wedding couple. A gift they will cherish for life.

descriptionShort: Wedbox is a beautiful wedding photo app that collects wedding photos from guests
title: Wedding Photo App by Wedbox

creator: Wedsly Wedding Apps
descriptionHtml:
Meet Wedbox - Your ultimate wedding day companion! 💖

Do you have an upcoming wedding and searching for a way to collect and share photos and videos of your special day? With Wedbox you can create a shared photo album where you and your guests can upload and download pictures and videos of your wedding day.

Explore all the features that Wedbox has to offer:

📸 Collaborative photo sharing
Invite your guests and even your professional wedding photographers to join Wedbox's shared photo album! They can upload their own pictures, ensuring that every beautiful snapshot is captured and shared. Your wedding memories are no longer confined to individual devices; they become a shared experience that can be cherished by all.

🎉 Fun and interactive Photo Booth
Add a touch of entertainment to your wedding reception with Wedbox's integrated photo booth feature. Just set up some light equipment and create some funny props and your guests will have a ton of fun!

🤩 Personal categorization of folders
Say goodbye to endless searching and scrolling! With Wedbox you can create a time schedule that sorts and categorizes your photos and videos from your wedding day, such as your rehearsal dinner, the ceremony, the reception, and the party. From the magical moments of your first dance to the joyous cake cutting, capturing, collecting and sharing your cherished wedding pictures and videos has never been simpler.

📅 View your Wedding Day Schedule
Wedbox allows you to map out your entire wedding day, ensuring that every moment can be captured as a picture or video. From the ceremony to the reception, you can rest assured that all of your special moments turn into wedding pictures that can be shared between you and your guests.

✅ Simplified Access with QR Codes
With Wedbox, sharing access to your wedding album is as easy as scanning a QR code. The app will generate a personalized QR code that you can share it with your guests. They can instantly access the app and explore the shared pictures and videos and upload their own images to your event.

📹 Share videos too!
Wedbox goes beyond photos and also supports video sharing. Relive your wedding day from start to finish by capturing not only the stills, but also the dynamic moments that makes your day truly extraordinary. Watch and share the highlights with your wedding guests.

💑 Interactive Guest engagement
Invite your guests to engage and share their thoughts through Wedbox's comment feature. Let your loved ones reminisce about those beautiful and joyous moments captured in pictures and videos. Share and celebrate the love and joy your wedding day brings together!

🥳 Also works for your bachelor or bachelorette
Why not use Wedbox for your Bachelor or Bachelorette? You can create more then one event in the app.

Use Wedbox and ensure that each photo and video of your wedding day is collected and shared between you, as the wedding couple, and your wedding guests. Collecting and sharing pictures and videos has never been simpler with Wedbox's easy-to-use features. Your event will already have a unique QR code so you good to go!

Download Wedbox and start an incredible journey of capturing and sharing the love and joy that your wedding day brings!

With Wedbox you can create a time schedule that sorts and categorizes your photos and videos from your wedding day, such as your rehearsal dinner, the ceremony, the reception, and the party. From the magical moments of your first dance to the joyous cake cutting, capturing, collecting and sharing your cherished wedding pictures and videos has never been simpler.

📅 View your Wedding Day Schedule
Wedbox allows you to map out your entire wedding day, ensuring that every moment can be captured as a picture or video. From the ceremony to the reception, you can rest assured that all of your special moments turn into wedding pictures that can be shared between you and your guests.

✅ Simplified Access with QR Codes
With Wedbox, sharing access to your wedding album is as easy as scanning a QR code. The app will generate a personalized QR code that you can share it with your guests. They can instantly access the app and explore the shared pictures and videos and upload their own images to your event.

📹 Share videos too!
Wedbox goes beyond photos and also supports video sharing. Relive your wedding day from start to finish by capturing not only the stills, but also the dynamic moments that makes your day truly extraordinary. Watch and share the highlights with your wedding guests.

💑 Interactive Guest engagement
Invite your guests to engage and share their thoughts through Wedbox's comment feature. Let your loved ones reminisce about those beautiful and joyous moments captured in pictures and videos. Share and celebrate the love and joy your wedding day brings together!

🥳 Also works for your bachelor or bachelorette
Why not use Wedbox for your Bachelor or Bachelorette? You can create more then one event in the app.

Use Wedbox and ensure that each photo and video of your wedding day is collected and shared between you, as the wedding couple, and your wedding guests. Collecting and sharing pictures and videos has never been simpler with Wedbox's easy-to-use features. Your event will already have a unique QR code so you good to go!

Download Wedbox and start an incredible journey of capturing and sharing the love and joy that your wedding day brings!
